<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3855203>
    dc:description "FIGURES 10–20. Stridulatory file below the left tegmen of Corycomima camerata (10); 11–14. Eulioptera spinulosa, male: habitus in lateral view (11), dorsal view (12) and lateral view (13) of last tergites, subgenital plate (14); 15–20. Paraeulioptera emitflesti Massa, n. gen. n. sp., male: habitus in lateral view (15), dorsal view of stridulatory area (16), fore femur and tibia (17), dorsal view of cerci (18), stridulatory file (19), lateral view of head and pronotum (20)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3855203/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

